<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.4.4">
<l>urakamellaṇai yāṉkaiyiluṟai caṅkampōlmaṭa vaṉṉaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>niraikaṇamparan tēṟuñceṅkama lavayaltiruk kōṭṭiyūr</l>
<l>narakanācaṉai nāvilkoṇṭaḻai yātamāṉiṭa cātiyar</l>
<l>parukunīrumu ṭukkuṅkūṟaiyum pāvañceytaṉa tāṅkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirukkōṭṭiyūr with red lotus fields</l>
<l>where flocks of simple swans,</l>
<l rend="indent">[each looking] like the conch that resides</l>
<l rend="indent">in the hand of he with the soft serpent bed,</l>
<l>fly up [and] spread out,</l>
<l>there is a caste of men who do not call out “Hell Destroyer”</l>
<l rend="indent">with [their] tongues,</l>
<l>[even] the water [they] drink and the clothes [they] wear</l>
<l rend="indent">are committing sins, are they not?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
